name: Pickled Freshwater Fillet
description: Pickled Freshwater Fillet is aFoodthat satisfiesHunger. It provides the uniqueStatus Effect,Pickled Freshwater Fillet, which increases maximumHealth, improvesStaminaand Health regeneration, and improves shared experience gain. Pickled Freshwater Fillet does not decay and is therefore useful for long-term storage.
